pakihi
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a large, low-lying area of leached soils with scanty natural growth of scrub, fern and rushes.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
